HEADWORD: Assimilative
<hw>As*sim"i*la*tive</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. LL.
<ets>assimilativus</ets>, F. <ets>assimilatif</ets>.]</ety> <def>Tending
